{"tid":989804,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"就住hkusu新莊，想做少少嘢","createTime":"2019-01-21T06:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T16:27:26.000Z","uid":132847,"like":89,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3e9b647e7a1ac0c3a6764801e778c145346724","tid":989804,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"今年班友幾離譜就大家都知，細佬我就諗緊有冇啲咩可以做到去阻止佢地當選。雖然宜家大學生通街都係，但如果連su都守唔住，咁香港就真係玩撚完。有冇咩方法可以有效阻止佢地當選？"},{"pid":"42db27b39d2b37938420554a72fc08c7e9a46754","tid":989804,"uid":176802,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"殺撚哂佢地"},{"pid":"d7e0da9cda7456ed38780105098c21973f62721d","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"投不信任票"},{"pid":"40d75dc9d86377a0de5a7f609fa4b0aa96c9cea7","tid":989804,"uid":132847,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"d7e0da9cda7456ed38780105098c21973f62721d","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"投不信任票"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"正路應該最好係投反對票，但仲要令啲港豬同學都投反對票"},{"pid":"381b80989f8b0e11bc66ba5198ef7013a18cc463","tid":989804,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"反對票"},{"pid":"28c675b447096177c77bc86e9e454e8c9ddd4181","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"40d75dc9d86377a0de5a7f609fa4b0aa96c9cea7","tid":989804,"uid":132847,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"d7e0da9cda7456ed38780105098c21973f62721d","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"投不信任票"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"正路應該最好係投反對票，但仲要令啲港豬同學都投反對票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:25:21.000Z","msg":"宣傳<br />\n- 民主牆大字報<br />\n- 遍地開花式A6海報<br />\n- 各電子平台出po<br />\n<br />\n內容 講多啲對家奶共野 文筆要專業 唔好用太明顯既搧情語氣<br />\n<br />\n另外形象都要顧 唔可以比對家差 所以相對強硬既宣傳手法 例如派傳單 洗班 之類 要睇住對家點做先決定自己點做 唔可以令自己形象差過對家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗成件事有四點要特別留意<br />\n1. 組織力 會唔會大家後繼無力/雷聲大雨點小<br />\n2. 建設性不信任 可能有同學會擔心無人當選咁會點算 宣傳內容一定要講acting幹事點產生 點解咁樣會好過比對家當選<br />\n3. 冷靜 對家有資源 後台同預先佈局都在暗 有咩變故一定要冷靜應對<br />\n4. 形象要show到真心 而唔係有班政棍仔搞亂檔 乘機上台"},{"pid":"059bfa8750573cd6f5a58271d1f179633e79c97a","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"樓主開完po之後已經後繼無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0d35b5397f3dc5c27f184027357af06ae9eac8","tid":989804,"uid":132847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"059bfa8750573cd6f5a58271d1f179633e79c97a","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"樓主開完po之後已經後繼無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"睇吓仲有冇咩討論同提議<br />\n我宜家搵緊啲fd，睇吓佢地點睇同有冇心一齊做啲嘢"},{"pid":"8b32f2919921fb4694dc48ec8cc3ea528ff3f493","tid":989804,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b0d35b5397f3dc5c27f184027357af06ae9eac8","tid":989804,"uid":132847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"059bfa8750573cd6f5a58271d1f179633e79c97a","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"樓主開完po之後已經後繼無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"睇吓仲有冇咩討論同提議<br />\n我宜家搵緊啲fd，睇吓佢地點睇同有冇心一齊做啲嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:30:29.000Z","msg":"咁有心力就一早出咗來選啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1b928a9c8fab0346770700ae13c83a0e91a123","tid":989804,"uid":147721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9b0d35b5397f3dc5c27f184027357af06ae9eac8","tid":989804,"uid":132847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"059bfa8750573cd6f5a